data.description: One of a kind, extraordinary, BREATHTAKING panoramic lake views from this luxurious home overlooking Lake Texoma. 1700 sf of open, wrap-around deck, perfect for entertaining or admiring sunrise AND sunset. Main level offers open floor plan, on-trend palette, wood floors & is basked with nature's grandeur through floor to ceiling picture windows. Chef’s white kitchen with quartz, island, ssa’s including 2 ovens & beverage fridge. Primary suite with private deck access, see-through fireplace, & ensuite bath with a lavish oversized walk-in shower & a standalone soaker tub. Lower level offers large living space with wet bar, laundry, storage, access to side flagstone patio, 2 bedrooms & full bath w quartz vanity & frameless shower. Nature beckons in backyard w luxurious zoysia grass, firepit & a canopy of trees. Convenient community boat ramp down the hill & marina 5 minutes away. Extensive improvements, from septic to proactive foundation repair have been meticulously tended to.
